## 7. Edge Cases & Known Limitations

| Scenario | Handling |
| --- | --- |
| **Reel from private account** | Reject at save time with user-friendly error. Show "Private Account" badge. |
| **Account goes private after save** | Content already transcribed and stored locally — chatbot still works. But "Open Reel" link will fail. Show warning badge on card. Future fix: detect and alert user. |
| **Reel is deleted after save** | Same as above — content preserved in DB, link dead. Show "Reel deleted" badge. |
| **No audio in Reel (text-only / visual content)** | Fall back to caption + hashtag analysis for categorization. Flag in UI: *"This Reel had no audio — categorized by caption."* |
| **Non-English Reel** | Whisper supports multilingual transcription. LLM handles multilingual categorization. MVP: best-effort, no language restriction. |
| **User never responds to uncategorized notification** | After 7 days, auto-assign to "Uncategorized." Re-attempt AI categorization weekly. |
| **Duplicate Reel saved** | Detect by reel_id. Show: *"You've already saved this Reel — it's in [Category]."* No duplicate stored. |
| **AI processing fails** | Mark as failed, retry up to 3 times. If still failing, notify user and save to Uncategorized with raw URL. |
| **Rate limits on OpenAI API** | BullMQ handles retries with exponential backoff. Queue design prevents thundering herd. |

