## 11. Risks

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Instagram breaks yt-dlp compatibility** | Medium | High | Pin yt-dlp version in production, monitor for failures, auto-update via CI job. Degrade gracefully: if download fails, save URL-only with a "pending" state and retry. |
| **Instagram rate-limits server IP** | Medium | High | Use rotating proxies or residential IP pool (e.g., Bright Data) for yt-dlp requests. Queue jobs with delay between requests. |
| **OpenAI API costs at scale** | Medium | Medium | Delete audio/video after transcription (don't store). Cache transcriptions — same reel URL = same content. Use GPT-4o-mini for categorization, GPT-4o only for chat. |
| **Auto-categorization accuracy below expectations** | Medium | Medium | Human-in-the-loop fallback (notification), user correction, weekly re-categorization of uncategorized items. |
| **App Store / Play Store rejection** | Low | High | Clear privacy policy, no hidden data collection, request only necessary permissions. |
| **Whisper accuracy for non-English / accent-heavy audio** | Low | Low | Whisper is multilingual and handles accents well. Flag low-confidence transcriptions in DB for monitoring. |

